{"tid":1578584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖921清牆其實係好事","createTime":"2019-09-18T07:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T10:53:04.000Z","uid":102527,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eeea9a979821aed61e048f3756d8cf05c17023d1","tid":1578584,"uid":102527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"眼見依加好多牆既資訊其實好亂好唔update<br />\n就算再貼新野上去啲人行過都會以為係old news<br />\n最多人關注既moment其實係岩岩新貼上去個陣由冇到有<br />\n佢哋主動幫手清其實係一件好事<br />\n<br />\n原因一：<br />\n<br />\n可以重新update番同promote新野<br />\n例如係黎緊929 101既野<br />\n俾人知道舊個啲已經清曬 依加個啲係新嘢未睇過<br />\n重新吸引人注意 可以用番啲舊有既策略 <br />\n例如係長輩圖大法 資訊牆<br />\n<br />\n原因二：<br />\n激發起大家文宣既心<br />\n其實依加已經越黎越少人貼牆 因為大家都覺得幅牆都貼滿左  唔使再貼都得 但同時亦都係造成文宣唔update既原因<br />\n所以一但何妖同佢班𡃁清到全港吉曬牆既話 <br />\n全世界都可以番番去當初文宣個步 幾日之內就令到全港多區都有野睇<br />\n<br />\n原因三：<br />\n你估貼容易啲定清容易啲<br />\n班老野曬住熱住咁清牆都攰死佢地啦<br />\n過兩日又周街都係仲唔激死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順便報個狗話有人有攻擊性武器（佢地清場個啲cutter）<br />\n唔講咩人 班狗以為係手足 實狗衝 到時發現係廢老們唔捉都夠撚狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以最後真係希望手足們汲取淘大教訓唔好硬碰，幫下手準備文宣既材料準備第日即刻貼番曬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"568535d3916874ef52bd53882a874a71c1babc81","tid":1578584,"uid":761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"等佢地清晒再一次過貼"},{"pid":"4ba1cd69a464448c6a35f4b13e57d2b62361e59c","tid":1578584,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"02885b0d63928b9531794de170bb4c8b3fbac854","tid":1578584,"uid":102527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7137d83c124a889b23d9e6512a33902f615ecd38","tid":1578584,"uid":204423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"由佢清，佢吹G做野，全世界黃c冇人理佢，922再貼過，吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想打大交，咪L旨意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10949aa7bb22d76dcaf33a6985a124b9e504f8e7","tid":1578584,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5708cd9ab8fb00a354fd6c54333c3e6174369b5a","tid":1578584,"uid":320135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"最緊要佢清得乾淨啲"},{"pid":"dcb4391ba68b8a27791db657d951cf3b0bceeb9c","tid":1578584,"uid":237645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"何大總統點會淨係清牆咁簡單<br />\n實帶埋班牛屎佬岀省城搞事"},{"pid":"6b96ff9e1752e1eb77ae9f0fdcece784a377711f","tid":1578584,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"清一貼十"},{"pid":"3a8f50fbcaf1f4af8e93cc1510db638bdafcd1c8","tid":1578584,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"如果咁岩路過見到佢地做清潔，我一定俾個Like佢！仲要講香港清潔最好有您！辛苦晒！"},{"pid":"c9ca3f8de5be590b316f93a8dddb26cc5b58729a","tid":1578584,"uid":59815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"印定22號貼"},{"pid":"fc1ec527946adbd659e044c111c3b2a2f979bd31","tid":1578584,"uid":102527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d1a37d3b8ba021377a9037c56d58d0d7a3f361b","tid":1578584,"uid":293161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"響應何妖活動第2彈: 香港修復日<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ebsfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ebsfvT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n之前想推921後一齊修復連儂牆但p牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c621423831f6b6eb3ca0fe6280d1f5792071e772","tid":1578584,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"文宣組可以重整文宣方向<br />\n等佢地清潔完後再貼"},{"pid":"63cbbf4b2098a5204f59dbf5096da2659e